WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
If you need to sell a house in Harrisburg, Pennsylvania, we can make you a simple cash offer and buy the property as is — meaning no repairs, no cleanup, and no open houses.

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:15.500
This can help if you inherited a house, have tenants you do not want to manage, are behind on payments, have code violations, or just need a clean way to move on.

00:00:15.500 --> 00:00:24.000
We handle houses across Harrisburg and Dauphin County, including older row homes, rentals, and properties that need work.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:32.500
There are no commissions, no agent showings, and no pressure. If the offer works for you, you choose the closing date.

00:00:32.500 --> 00:00:39.400
Call eight eight eight, two seven four, five zero zero six, and we will walk you through your options.
